@SalesCobrosGeo.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5207
@Token = REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN

### Login as admin
POST {{SalesCobrosGeo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "admin.demo",
  "password": "demo123"
}

### Current user
GET {{SalesCobrosGeo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### Sales team view (supervisor/admin)
GET {{SalesCobrosGeo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/sales/team
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### Register payment (collector/supervisor/admin)
POST {{SalesCobrosGeo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/collections/register?saleId=1001&amount=50
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### Audit recent (admin only)
GET {{SalesCobrosGeo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/audit/recent?take=20
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
